venue.name: Saint Anselm College - New Hampshire Institute of Politics

item.description:
Eric Rosengren, president and CEO of the Federal Reserve Bank of Boston will meet with The Business and Industry Association of New Hampshire and Bankers Association members over lunch to discuss New England's economy and related economic matters.

Let's let them know how we feel about the FED.

If you are so inclined to purchase a ticket to go inside for the luncheon here is the link to do so: http://www.biaofnh.com/cwt/External/WCPages/WCEvents/EventDetail.aspx?EventID=152

*Please note, pre registration will close at 3:00pm on Wednesday, March 26th.*

More info here: https://www.facebook.com/events/580586618626919/permalink/580614138624167/?notif_t=like
